billEvents.eventText: REFERRED TO CORPORATIONS, AUTHORITIES AND COMMISSIONS

title: Establishes a kitchen incubator/shared-use kitchen facility program within the urban development corporation
summary: Establishes a kitchen incubator/shared-use kitchen facility program within the urban development corporation; provides grant funding to local development corporations, municipalities, educational institutions and not-for-profit entities for the development or expansion of kitchen incubator/shared-use kitchen facilities which make available services such as food production, technical assistance, business management and marketing, distribution, storage and retailing assistance, particularly in economically distressed areas.
lawSection: New York State Urban Development Corporation Act
actClause: AN ACT to amend chapter 174 of the laws of 1968 constituting the New York state urban development corporation act, in relation to kitchen incubator/shared-use kitchen facilities
